items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        namespace: estafette
        env:

items.manifestWithDefaults:
builder:
  track: dev
labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  language: golang
  team: estafette-team
version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master
stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette
  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette
  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'failed'
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev
        shell: /bin/sh
        workDir: /estafette-work
        when: status == 'succeeded'
      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        shell: /bin/bash
        workDir: /estafette-work
        commands:
        - apk add --update --no-cache gettext
        - gcloud components install kubectl
        - echo "${GCLOUD_KEY_FILE}" | base64 -d > key-file.json
        - gcloud auth activate-service-account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME} --key-file ./key-file.json
        - gcloud config set account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME}
        - gcloud config set project ${GCLOUD_PROJECT_NAME}
        - gcloud container clusters get-credentials ${GCLOUD_GKE_CLUSTER_NAME} --zone
          ${GCLOUD_GKE_ZONE}
        - cat kubernetes.yaml | envsubst | kubectl apply -f -
        - kubectl rollout status deploy/estafette-ci-api -n estafette
        when: status == 'succeeded'
        env:

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        namespace: estafette

  app-group: estafette-ci
  language: golang
  team: estafette-team
version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master
stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette
  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette
  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'failed'
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev
        shell: /bin/sh
        workDir: /estafette-work
        when: status == 'succeeded'
      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        shell: /bin/bash
        workDir: /estafette-work
        commands:
        - apk add --update --no-cache gettext
        - gcloud components install kubectl
        - echo "${GCLOUD_KEY_FILE}" | base64 -d > key-file.json
        - gcloud auth activate-service-account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME} --key-file ./key-file.json
        - gcloud config set account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME}
        - gcloud config set project ${GCLOUD_PROJECT_NAME}
        - gcloud container clusters get-credentials ${GCLOUD_GKE_CLUSTER_NAME} --zone
          ${GCLOUD_GKE_ZONE}
        - cat kubernetes.yaml | envsubst | kubectl apply -f -
        - kubectl rollout status deploy/estafette-ci-api -n estafette
        when: status == 'succeeded'

commits.message: add auth middleware and create release endpoint

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        namespace: estafette
        env:

items.manifestWithDefaults:
builder:
  track: dev
labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  language: golang
  team: estafette-team
version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master
stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette
  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette
  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'failed'
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev
        shell: /bin/sh
        workDir: /estafette-work
        when: status == 'succeeded'
      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        shell: /bin/bash
        workDir: /estafette-work
        commands:
        - apk add --update --no-cache gettext
        - gcloud components install kubectl
        - echo "${GCLOUD_KEY_FILE}" | base64 -d > key-file.json
        - gcloud auth activate-service-account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME} --key-file ./key-file.json
        - gcloud config set account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME}

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine

items.manifestWithDefaults:
builder:
  track: dev
labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  language: golang
  team: estafette-team
version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master
stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette
  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette
  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'failed'
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev
        shell: /bin/sh
        workDir: /estafette-work
        when: status == 'succeeded'
      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        shell: /bin/bash
        workDir: /estafette-work
        commands:
        - apk add --update --no-cache gettext
        - gcloud components install kubectl
        - echo "${GCLOUD_KEY_FILE}" | base64 -d > key-file.json
        - gcloud auth activate-service-account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME} --key-file ./key-file.json
        - gcloud config set account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME}
        - gcloud config set project ${GCLOUD_PROJECT_NAME}
        - gcloud container clusters get-credentials ${GCLOUD_GKE_CLUSTER_NAME} --zone
          ${GCLOUD_GKE_ZONE}
        - cat kubernetes.yaml | envsubst | kubectl apply -f -
        - kubectl rollout status deploy/estafette-ci-api -n estafette
        when: status == 'succeeded'
        env:

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        namespace: estafette

    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette
  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'failed'
    channels:
    - '#build-status'

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        namespace: estafette

items.manifestWithDefaults:
builder:
  track: dev
labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  language: golang
  team: estafette-team
version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master
stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette
  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette
  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'failed'
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev
        shell: /bin/sh
        workDir: /estafette-work
        when: status == 'succeeded'
      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        shell: /bin/bash
        workDir: /estafette-work
        commands:
        - apk add --update --no-cache gettext
        - gcloud components install kubectl
        - echo "${GCLOUD_KEY_FILE}" | base64 -d > key-file.json
        - gcloud auth activate-service-account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME} --key-file ./key-file.json
        - gcloud config set account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME}
        - gcloud config set project ${GCLOUD_PROJECT_NAME}
        - gcloud container clusters get-credentials ${GCLOUD_GKE_CLUSTER_NAME} --zone
          ${GCLOUD_GKE_ZONE}
        - cat kubernetes.yaml | envsubst | kubectl apply -f -
        - kubectl rollout status deploy/estafette-ci-api -n estafette
        when: status == 'succeeded'
        env:

commits.message: use queryrow when 1 record is expected

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        namespace: estafette

    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette
  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'failed'
    channels:
    - '#build-status'

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine

items.manifestWithDefaults:
builder:
  track: dev
labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  language: golang
  team: estafette-team
version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master
stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette
  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette
  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'failed'
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev
        shell: /bin/sh
        workDir: /estafette-work
        when: status == 'succeeded'
      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        shell: /bin/bash
        workDir: /estafette-work
        commands:
        - apk add --update --no-cache gettext
        - gcloud components install kubectl
        - echo "${GCLOUD_KEY_FILE}" | base64 -d > key-file.json
        - gcloud auth activate-service-account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME} --key-file ./key-file.json
        - gcloud config set account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME}
        - gcloud config set project ${GCLOUD_PROJECT_NAME}
        - gcloud container clusters get-credentials ${GCLOUD_GKE_CLUSTER_NAME} --zone
          ${GCLOUD_GKE_ZONE}
        - cat kubernetes.yaml | envsubst | kubectl apply -f -
        - kubectl rollout status deploy/estafette-ci-api -n estafette
        when: status == 'succeeded'
        env:

Merge pull request #28 from estafette/release-via-estafette

Release via estafette

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 1
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        namespace: estafette

    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette
  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'failed'
    channels:
    - '#build-status'

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 0
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine

items.manifestWithDefaults:
builder:
  track: dev
labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  language: golang
  team: estafette-team
version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 0
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master
stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette
  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette
  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'failed'
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev
        shell: /bin/sh
        workDir: /estafette-work
        when: status == 'succeeded'
      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:215.0.0-alpine
        shell: /bin/bash
        workDir: /estafette-work
        commands:
        - apk add --update --no-cache gettext
        - gcloud components install kubectl
        - echo "${GCLOUD_KEY_FILE}" | base64 -d > key-file.json
        - gcloud auth activate-service-account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME} --key-file ./key-file.json
        - gcloud config set account ${GCLOUD_SA_NAME}
        - gcloud config set project ${GCLOUD_PROJECT_NAME}
        - gcloud container clusters get-credentials ${GCLOUD_GKE_CLUSTER_NAME} --zone
          ${GCLOUD_GKE_ZONE}
        - cat kubernetes.yaml | envsubst | kubectl apply -f -
        - kubectl rollout status deploy/estafette-ci-api -n estafette
        when: status == 'succeeded'
        env:

commits.message: actually apply manifest during release

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 0
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'

releases:
  tooling:
    stages:
      git-clone:
        image: extensions/git-clone:dev

      deploy:
        image: google/cloud-sdk:213.0.0-alpine
        namespace: estafette

items.manifestWithDefaults:
builder:
  track: dev
labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  language: golang
  team: estafette-team
version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 0
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master
stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION}
      -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH}
      -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
      .
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    when: status == 'succeeded'
    action: build
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    path: ./publish
    repositories:
    - estafette

    action: push

commits.message: release via estafette; show rendered manifest

items.manifest:
builder:
  track: dev

labels:
  app: estafette-ci-api
  app-group: estafette-ci
  team: estafette-team
  language: golang

version:
  semver:
    major: 0
    minor: 0
    patch: '{{auto}}'
    labelTemplate: '{{branch}}'
    releaseBranch: master

stages:
  build:
    image: golang:1.10.3-alpine3.8
    workDir: /go/src/github.com/estafette/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    commands:
    - go test `go list ./... | grep -v /vendor/`
    - CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -a -installsuffix cgo -ldflags "-X main.version=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_VERSION} -X main.revision=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_REVISION} -X main.branch=${ESTAFETTE_GIT_BRANCH} -X main.buildDate=${ESTAFETTE_BUILD_DATETIME}" -o ./publish/${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP} .

  bake:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: build
    repositories:
    - estafette
    path: ./publish
    copy:
    - Dockerfile
    - /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

  push-to-docker-hub:
    image: extensions/docker:dev
    action: push
    repositories:
    - estafette
    when:
      status == 'succeeded' &&
      branch == 'master' &&
      server == 'gocd'

  slack-notify:
    image: extensions/slack-build-status:dev
    webhook: estafette.secret(08UOJSF6Fvdz9u2X.lzsCArDpf97g7i2Vx-3UTyWsxCB81e05jthdY_AI3OffXBA-NurQePraQqzNf-9IhdoDvr1Akg0yom4S2kHjvWLhRC8Y7xgheK8MR6qPu2oi3QvlYbnNtTTOOjMi)
    name: ${ESTAFETTE_LABEL_APP}
    channels:
    - '#build-status'
    when:
      status == 'failed'
